## 1.How to install python boto3 on ubuntu

Successfully installed boto3-1.35.76 botocore-1.35.76 jmespath-1.0.1 python-dateutil-2.9.0.post0 s3transfer-0.10.4 six-1.17.0 urllib3-2.2.3
(myenv) ubuntu@ip-172-31-86-180:~$ python3 -c "import boto3; print(boto3.__version__)"
1.35.76
(myenv) ubuntu@ip-172-31-86-180:~$ history
1  clear
2  sudo apt update
3  sudo apt install python3 python3-pip -y
4  sudo apt install python3-venv -y
5  python3 --version
6  pip3 --version
7  python3 -m venv myenv
8  source myenv/bin/activate
9  pip install boto3
10  python3 -c "import boto3; print(boto3.__version__)"
11  history

(myenv) ubuntu@ip-172-31-86-180:~$

